<p style="margin: 5px 0;">1. Ask me questions about what my test is trying to verify</p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0;">2. Help me identify if my test is checking behavior or implementation details</p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0;">3. Suggest how I could make the test's purpose clearer</p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0;">4. Ask me what edge cases my test might be missing</p>
