<h4 style="color: #141312; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.3em; margin-bottom: 15px;">How This Helps You Learn:</h4>
<ul style="color: #141312; padding-left: 20px;">
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Focuses on improving one test deeply rather than having many superficial tests</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Teaches you to write more meaningful and robust tests</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Helps you understand the difference between testing behavior vs. implementation</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Builds your skills in writing clear, maintainable tests</li>
</ul>
