<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Develops your ability to think in small, testable increments</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Builds understanding of the red-green-refactor cycle</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Creates good TDD habits from the beginning</li>
</ul>
</div>
