<h2 style="color: #f09b08; font-size: 2.2em; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #F09B08; padding-bottom: 15px;">A Principle Discovered: Learn Through Guided Practice</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #141312;">In this chapter, weŌĆÖve applied the principle of learning through guided practice. Instead of having AI generate complete solutions, we use it to ask questions, provide focused guidance, and offer feedback on our work.</p>
<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 5px solid #F09B08; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1em; color: #141312;">This approach helps develop critical thinking and problem-solving skills rather than creating dependency. By asking AI to guide rather than generate, youŌĆÖre building lasting skills that will serve you throughout your career.</p>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #141312;">Remember that the goal isnŌĆÖt just to produce tests but to become a developer who thinks deeply about code quality and correctness. Using AI as a learning partner rather than a code generator will help you reach that goal.</p>
<div style="background-color: #141312; color: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center;">
